dublin_core.dcvalue: Significant information is available about government reimbursed telehealth services such as Medicare and Medicaid across the United States Although currently 20 states mandate reimbursement for telehealth services and some private insurers have voluntarily covered those services in other states relatively little is known about telehealth provider experiences with reimbursement from private insurance payers
